<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><title>$ command line ruby cheat sheets</title><link charset="utf-8" href="/style.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /></head><body><div class="main"><div class="header"><h1><a href="/">cheat sheets.</a></h1><code class="header">$ command line ruby cheat sheets</code></div></div><div class="content"><pre>Setup
-----
# Assuming you have Ruby+Gems

gem install vagrant
vagrant box add precise64 http://files.vagrantup.com/precise64.box
mkdir precise64
cd precise64
vagrant init precise64
vagrant up
vagrant ssh

# precise64 folder will be mapped to /vagrant folder on machine



Commands
--------

$ vagrant --help

     box
     destroy
     gem
     halt
     init
     package
     provision
     reload
     resume
     ssh
     ssh-config
     status
     suspend
     up

# For help on any individual command run `vagrant COMMAND -h`



General Info
------------

# Vagrant files are stored on your user dir
ls ~/.vagrant.d/

# Vagrant boxes dir (for distributing/sharing)
ls ~/.vagrant.d/boxes/



Boxes addresses
---------------
http://www.vagrantbox.es/



Update VirtBox Guest Additions:
-------------------------------
from: https://github.com/mitchellh/vagrant/issues/355

  On Virtual box:    
    $ /etc/init.d/vboxadd setup

  In working dir:    
    $ vagrant reload</pre></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="footer">Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/">Sinatra</a>,
